    <item>
      <title>特朗普依靠国会来解决他关于选民欺诈的虚假指控</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/02/24/us/politics/trump-congress-voting-save-america-act.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国情咨文为总统提供了一个高调的机会，呼吁他对选举安全立法采取行动，他曾向共和党人施压，要求他们压倒民主党的反对派。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/02/24/us/politics/trump-congress-voting-save-america-act.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 24 Feb 2026 18:50:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普将向自满的国会发表讲话，国会在他的议程上存在严重分歧</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/02/24/us/congress-trump-state-of-the-union.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[特朗普总统将向立法机构发表讲话，该机构已将大部分权力让渡给他，但最近又温和地予以反击，而且在中期选举之前，党派分歧比以往任何时候都更深。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/02/24/us/congress-trump-state-of-the-union.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 24 Feb 2026 16:27:05 GMT</pubDate>
